data.description: This one and a half story home offers just under 3000 sq ft of space. Inside you will be greeted by an open design with a large living area adjacent to a grand kitchen with granite counter tops, oversized island and beautiful white cabinetry. The master suite and two generously sized secondary bedrooms are located on the first floor. Upstairs you will find a private bedroom complete with full bath and loft area. The back yard features a newly installed composite deck perfect for entertaining and outdoor BBQs.
